{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "attachments": [{"creator": "cam@mcc.id.au", "is_obsolete": 1, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8746456}, {"creator": "cam@mcc.id.au", "is_obsolete": 1, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2016-04-28T18:26:58Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2016-04-28T09:41:32Z", "id": 1384646, "setter": "bobbyholley@gmail.com"}], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8746457}, {"creator": "cam@mcc.id.au", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2016-04-29T01:52:08Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2016-04-29T01:30:07Z", "id": 1385252, "setter": "bobbyholley@gmail.com"}], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8746888}, {"creator": "cam@mcc.id.au", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8746889}], "classification": "Components", "creator": "cam@mcc.id.au", "cc": ["bobbyholley@gmail.com"], "depends_on": [], "creation_time": "2016-04-28T09:11:01Z", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "Unspecified", "cf_status_firefox58": "---", "cf_status_firefox59": "---", "keywords": [], "summary": "implement ServoStyleSet::ResolveStyleForNonElement for text nodes", "id": 1268404, "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 54040, "name": "cam@mcc.id.au", "real_name": "Cameron McCormack (:heycam) (away for the moment)"}, "severity": "normal", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "assigned_to": "cam@mcc.id.au", "comment_count": 11, "comments": [{"text": "", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11364231, "time": "2016-04-28T09:11:01Z"}, {"text": "https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=847b89c7c8e5", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11364297, "time": "2016-04-28T09:40:42Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8746456\nPart 1: Pass text node into ResolveStyleForNonElement.", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11364298, "time": "2016-04-28T09:41:10Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8746457\nPart 2: Implement ServoStyleSet::ResolveStyleForNonElement for text nodes.", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11364300, "time": "2016-04-28T09:41:32Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8746456\nPart 1: Pass text node into ResolveStyleForNonElement.\n\nReview of attachment 8746456:\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n::: layout/style/nsStyleSet.h\n@@ +173,5 @@\n>    // any rule matching for them is a first step.\n>    // When text-combine-upright is not present, we may also want to avoid\n>    // resolving style contexts for text frames as well.\n>    already_AddRefed<nsStyleContext>\n> +  ResolveStyleForNonElement(nsIContent* aContent,\n\nWorth adding a comment about exactly what aContent refers to here, and when it is and isn't null.\n\nThough to be honest, I think it would be cleaner to just have ResolveStyleForTextNode(nsIContent* aTextNode, nsStyleContext* aParentContext), and leave ResolveStyleForNonElement the way it is. This would avoid having a bunch of callers pass nullptr for the contextually-meaningless parameter.\n\nThe nsStyleSet implementation is pretty barebones, and our Servo implementation for these two cases seems like it's going to be pretty orthogonal.\n\nWhat do you think?", "author": "bobbyholley@gmail.com", "id": 11366629, "time": "2016-04-28T18:22:38Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8746457\nPart 2: Implement ServoStyleSet::ResolveStyleForNonElement for text nodes.\n\nReview of attachment 8746457:\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nr=me modulo the discussion regarding the previous patch.", "author": "bobbyholley@gmail.com", "id": 11366652, "time": "2016-04-28T18:26:58Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Bobby Holley (busy) from comment #4)\n> Though to be honest, I think it would be cleaner to just have\n> ResolveStyleForTextNode(nsIContent* aTextNode, nsStyleContext*\n> aParentContext), and leave ResolveStyleForNonElement the way it is. This\n> would avoid having a bunch of callers pass nullptr for the\n> contextually-meaningless parameter.\n\nSounds fair.", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11367905, "time": "2016-04-29T00:20:58Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8746888\nPart 1: Split out ResolveStyleForText from ResolveStyleForNonEleme nt and pass in the text node.", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11368073, "time": "2016-04-29T01:30:07Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8746889\nPart 2: Implement ServoStyleSet::ResolveStyleForText. r=bholley", "author": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 11368074, "time": "2016-04-29T01:30:31Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/integration/mozilla-inbound/rev/1befe70618d1\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/integration/mozilla-inbound/rev/cadc30c3f197", "author": "pulsebot@bots.tld", "id": 11368304, "time": "2016-04-29T04:21:19Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/1befe70618d1\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/cadc30c3f197", "author": "kwierso@gmail.com", "id": 11371002, "time": "2016-04-29T22:02:19Z"}], "cf_last_resolved": "2016-04-29T22:02:19Z", "priority": "--", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "unspecified", "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox59": "---", "last_change_time": "2016-04-29T22:02:19Z", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "---", "blocks": [1243581], "qa_contact": "", "see_also": [], "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "component": "CSS Parsing and Computation", "votes": 0, "cf_status_firefox49": "fixed", "groups": [], "cf_status_firefox60": "---", "target_milestone": "mozilla49", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_status_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "url": "", "creator_detail": {"email": "cam@mcc.id.au", "id": 54040, "name": "cam@mcc.id.au", "real_name": "Cameron McCormack (:heycam) (away for the moment)"}, "whiteboard": "", "mentors": [], "cc_d